      <para id="id316351">After <m:math><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mspace width="2pt"/><m:mi>s</m:mi></m:math>, pulse A has moved <m:math><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mspace width="2pt"/><m:mi>m</m:mi></m:math> to the right and pulse B has moved <m:math><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mspace width="2pt"/><m:mi>m</m:mi></m:math> to the left.</para>
